### Test Document Search Endpoints

### 1. Search documents with keyword (Student/Teacher)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/documents/search?q=math
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 2. Search in specific class
GET http://localhost:5000/api/documents/search?q=assignment&classId=YOUR_CLASS_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 3. List documents with search filter and pagination
GET http://localhost:5000/api/documents?search=exam&page=1&limit=10&sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 4. List all documents (Student - only their class)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/documents
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 5. List all documents (Teacher - only their documents)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/documents
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 6. Search with multiple keywords
GET http://localhost:5000/api/documents/search?q=homework
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

